default2.1.1
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultEnsuring resilience of the strategic road network is a challenge during times of severe weather
default, especially as 
defaultweather conditions can be unpredictable and change quickly.  High traffic volumes and congestion, particularly at peak times, can make keeping th
defaulte network open during severe weather difficult.  However, this is what the Agency aims to achieve and it has done so consistently over recent years with only very isolated problems at times of exceptionally extreme weather.
